paint.shared.utils

Class Miscellaneous

  • java.lang.Object
    • paint.shared.utils.Miscellaneous

  • public final class Miscellaneous
extends Object
    Static utility class containing miscellaneous helper methods used across PAINT modules.

    Provides methods for time formatting, numeric rounding, and robust boolean string parsing.

        public static boolean isBooleanValue(String value)
        Evaluates a string as a boolean. Supports variations such as "true", "yes", "y", "1" for true and "false", "no", "n", "0" for false. Invalid values log an error via PaintLogger.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        boolean interpretation of the input
